---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Belong">
  <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4 py-20 space-y-10">
    <h1 class="font-['Newsreader'] text-5xl md:text-6xl font-bold text-[#0F2830]">Belong</h1>

    <section class="bg-white border-2 border-[#0F2830] p-8">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-[#0F2830] mb-3">Midweek Groups</h2>
      <p class="mb-3 text-[#0F2830]/90">We encourage anyone part of our church family to find transformation, discipleship, and growth in a small community.</p>
      <p class="mb-3 text-[#0F2830]/90">Most of our communities meet weekly to study God's Word, pray, and encourage one another in faith.</p>
      <p class="text-[#0F2830]/90">To join a community, please <a href="/contact" class="underline decoration-[#45B074] underline-offset-4">contact us</a>.</p>
    </section>

    <section class="bg-white border-2 border-[#0F2830] p-8">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-[#0F2830] mb-3">Kids</h2>
      <p class="text-[#0F2830]/90">We have kids groups (ages 1-11) that meet during our Sunday gathering. Speak to our welcome team to find out more.</p>
    </section>

    <section class="bg-white border-2 border-[#0F2830] p-8">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-[#0F2830] mb-3">Youth (Cornerstone)</h2>
      <p class="mb-3 text-[#0F2830]/90">Our youth group Cornerstone meets every Wednesday at church from 6:00-7:00pm. If you are at secondary school, we would love to see you there.</p>
      <p class="text-[#0F2830]/90">We also run a youth Bible study during selected Sunday gatherings for Years 7-10.</p>
    </section>
  </div>
</Layout>
